'''''Kanna Thorakkanum Saami''''' ({{trans|Open your eyes, man}}) is a [[1986 in film|1986]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by R.Govindraj for Punitha Cine Arts. The film stars [[Sivakumar]] and [[Jeevitha]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Kanna Thorakkanum Saami LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/412/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-05-02|}}</ref>

